com.liquidm.sdk
Class NativeAdViewFiller

java.lang.Object
  com.liquidm.sdk.NativeAdViewFiller

public class NativeAdViewFiller
extends Object

A tool that propagates native ad view with native ad data.
NativeAdViewFiller:

  • searches for asset view having tag equal to asset name
    (this can be configured by setting custom NativeAdViewFiller.AssetViewFinder with setAssetViewFinder(AssetViewFinder))
  • fills asset view with asset data using appropriate NativeAdViewFiller.AssetViewFiller
    (NativeAdViewFiller.AssetViewFillers for TextView, ImageView and Button are set by default, custom ones can be set using setAssetViewFiller(Class, AssetViewFiller))
  • attaches impression tracker to native ad view
    (using ViewTreeObserver.addOnPreDrawListener(android.view.ViewTreeObserver.OnPreDrawListener))
  • attaches click handlers to asset views
    (unless they are ignored using setIgnoreAssetViewClicks(String, boolean))
  • allows to listen for events using NativeAdListener
NativeAdViewFiller can be used repeatedly for filling in the same native ad view with different native ad data.
